{"type":"article_comment","id":391493,"parentType":"article","parentId":19449,"uid":50178,"contents":"我建议反贼们不要着急，未来十年是中国财政崩塌的十年，谁在台上都是架在火上烤，贪吃蛇自己会把自己吃掉。&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n2021年就进入严重老龄化，1961年出生高峰的人退休，退休人员暴增3倍持续十年，估计等到1973年高峰回落的人退休，毛都不剩了<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Birth_rate_in_China.svg/450px-Birth_rate_in_China.svg.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Birth_rate_in_China.svg/450px-Birth_rate_in_China.svg.png\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Birth_rate_in_China.svg/450px-Birth_rate_in_China.svg.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-05-27","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}